data.description: MOVE IN READY CalAtlantic home in Five Oaks Crossing!! Beautiful 2-story offers 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, an executive study, upstairs game and media rooms, and an oversized 2-car garage! Open concept notable upon entry with dramatic 2-story ceilings in foyer & vaulted ceilings with cedar beam in study. Gourmet island kitchen connects to elegant dining room with tray ceilings. Family room open to kitchen & dining, making space feel large and bold with 2-story ceilings that open to the 2nd floor and high windows on surrounding walls. The master suite is located in the corner of the home for privacy and provides great views of the backyard from the cozy window seat. B-vent gas FP with electronic ignition!
